      "date": "2015-08-24 16:03:29.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n(2 comments)\n\nOleg,\n\nI have answered your questions inline, please see below.\n\nHowever, now that we finally got all tests to pass, and got all positive inspections, can we consider landing this patch now, and push a new patch with the modifications you suggest? Moreover, given that the modifications you suggest are beyond the scope of this patch aiming at addressing the encpool issue, I would prefer to push a separate patch.\n\nWhat do you think?",
